==Preparation==
{{See also|Treasure Trails/Guide/Emote clues/Items}}
[[Clue scroll (medium)|Medium clue scrolls]] can be between three and five clues long with some quest requirements.

{|class="wikitable align-center-1"
! colspan=2 | Item
! Description
|-
| {{plinkt|Clue scroll (medium)|txt=Clue scroll}}
| Must be in the inventory in order to receive the next step or reward.
|-
| {{plinkt|Spade}}
| Digging in certain locations is required for some clues.
|-
| {{plinkp|Law rune}} {{plinkp|Amulet of glory(4)}}
| [[Teleportation]] [[runes]] and enchanted [[jewellery]]
| Use this to travel over large distances.
|-
| {{plinkp|Energy potion}} {{plinkp|Super energy}} {{plinkp|Stamina potion}}
| [[Energy potion]]s ([[Super energy potion|super]]) or [[stamina potion]]s
| Use these to restore [[energy]].
|-
| {{plinkp|Coins|pic=Coins 10000}}
| [[Money]]
| Use this to buy items needed for [[emote clues]] and travel costs.
|-
| {{plinkp|Dramen staff}} {{plinkp|Lunar staff}}{{Plinkp|Explorer's ring 4}}
| [[Dramen staff|Dramen]]/ [[lunar staff]] or [[Lumbridge & Draynor Elite Diary]]
| Use this to access the [[Fairy ring]] network shortly into [[Fairytale II - Cure a Queen]] (especially useful for [[medium clue]]s).
|-
| {{plinkp|Dragon scimitar}}
| [[Weapon]]
| Some clue steps require combat.
|}

